780
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,680
 što pretražuju.

781
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:46,920
 Dakle.

782
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:50,440
 Ako neko pretražuje pojam Hrvatska u Britaniji,

