791
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:13,980
 Mi smo to uočili prije četiri godine.

792
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:16,560
 To sam vam u krizi Big Crisis Data

793
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:19,360
 znači detaljno opisao tu metodologiju

794
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:21,160
 koja pokazuje da nije točno

795
